693
00:26:47.890 --> 00:26:49.009
Tiene miedo,

694
00:26:49.410 --> 00:26:50.770
se dijo Rascónicov.

695
00:26:51.625 --> 00:26:54.505
Sacó suavemente el hacha del mudo corredizo y

696
00:26:54.505 --> 00:26:56.585
le dio 2 golpes en la coronilla,

697
00:26:56.904 --> 00:26:58.585
pero, cosa extraña,

698
00:26:58.825 --> 00:27:01.224
